QuestData.Title: Ruumbo Demands Honey
QuestData.Description: Ruumbo hungers!$B$BThe Deadwood jerks have stolen all their honey from the Timbermaw tribe! We saw...er, Ruumbo saw them do it! Now Ruumbo must have that honey!$B$BTake this... this stick! Yes, this stick. Take this stick and use it to steal the honey from their beehives in Deadwood Village.$B$BRuumbo must have as much honey as possible. This is vital.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 10 Deadwood Honey Globs from the hives in Deadwood Village using Ruumbo's Honey Stick.
QuestData.CompletionText: Ruumbo can smell whether you have honey or not!
QuestData.RewardText: Honey! Delicious honey!$B$BWell done, ugly creature! You may put the honey...put the honey down right there. No, to the left. Yes, there. Just leave it there.
